data.description: Bring your horses and enjoy your own slice of farm life on this charming 1.84 acre property with a peaceful shared pond and beautifully updated home in Haslet Park. Gorgeous wood-look Luxury Vinyl Plank floors flow thru-out this desirable open concept living, kitchen and dining area. Create memories to last a lifetime gathered in the living room with a cozy wood burning fireplace. Make your way into the gourmet kitchen offering Quartz counter-tops, Samsung ss appliances, and farmhouse light fixture highlighting the bfast bar. The secluded primary bedroom is split from the secondary rooms and has 2 WIC's for ample storage. This wonderful property has a covered patio and gazebo with plenty of grass for kids and pets to play. The 60x26 metal barn houses 3, 13x12 board on board stalls with custom fit rubber mats. Additional features include a full pasture, 84x48 small turn-out, riding pad, and covered hayfeeder. SELLER IS OFFERING A $10K CREDIT TOWARDS RATE BUYDOWN OR CLOSING COSTS.
